    flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Init Shared State]
    B --> C[Invoke Decide Prompt]
    C --> D[Parse YAML Output]
    D -->|Malformed| E[Repair & Retry]
    E --> D
    D -->|Valid| F{Action Token?}
    F -->|search| G[Call Web Search]
    G --> H[Append Results]
    H --> C
    F -->|answer| I[Generate Final Answer]
    I --> J([Return Done])